{"tid":1210443,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（各有辦法）潘生潘太出黎回應啦！推","createTime":"2019-06-12T13:46:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T13:57:33.000Z","uid":115815,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9fef2f757e9c950222ad879eb5d15af5ac63b754","tid":1210443,"uid":115815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T13:46:37.000Z","msg":"希望各路方法一齊上<br />\n做到咩就試下做啦<br />\n唔做仲係到等死？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請大家幫幫手</span><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>除了西環的街坊發起聯署，就<span style=\"color: red;\">連台灣謀殺案遇害港人潘曉穎的居所，觀塘私人屋苑麗港城</span>也有街坊發起了反對修訂《逃犯條例》的網上聯署。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n潘生潘太應該係住麗港城<br />\n有無住麗港城手足可以聯絡到佢地出來講兩句</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n阿潘生阿潘太 不如你地出黎講下野啦 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1209247\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1209247</a> - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0ff4f5240e2c700a392eb10d0fad5613ad9c33fd","tid":1210443,"uid":115815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T13:49:34.000Z","msg":"手足幫幫手啦"},{"pid":"c79c44e460154425286392022dd9e93754beecfb","tid":1210443,"uid":115815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T13:56:50.000Z","msg":"推呀推"},{"pid":"060b5368f83e732be1c8e5610e597e7949416fc0","tid":1210443,"uid":189430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T13:57:33.000Z","msg":"你仲點會搵到佢地<br />\n俾人被消失左都唔奇啦"}]}